extends layout

block content
  h3= title
  p This app helps you to keep track of all read books, as well as of ones on the wish list.

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Books:] !{data.book_count}
      li #[strong Authors:] !{data.author_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}
      li #[strong Languages:] !{data.language_count}
      li #[strong Countries:] !{data.country_count}